metadata.symbol: Designed with love by Geeky KiKi
metadata.description:
Meet Bubbly Berry!  We hope our limited-edition collectible Cutiecoin NFTs will bring you happy, abundant success.  

This is a special prelaunch with our top three beloved Cutiecoins NFTs for our friends and family. We will never mint Cute Cupcake, Bubbly Berry, or Shooting Star again.

The first three to bid on each new Cutiecoin will be mailed a swag bag of cute stickers and pins.

20% of the sale$, will go to the final bidder's charity of choice. We will DM you.

Thank you in advance for believing in the success of Cutiecoins and placing your bids!  Artist bio on Instagram @missgeekykiki
